FBIS4-61348 "drsov087_v_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-087 Daily Report 4 May 1994 Lithuania President Welcomes Israel-PLO Agreement President Welcomes Israel-PLO Agreement WS0505091894 Vilnius ELTA in English 1715 GMT 4 May 94 WS0505091894 Vilnius ELTA English BFN [From "News Bulletin" No. 492] [Text] Vilnius, May 4, ELTA -- Lithuanian President Algirdas Brazauskas sent congratulations for Israeli president and PLO leader Yasir 'Arafat on the occasion of signing the agreement on the Palestinian self-rule. Brazauskas noted in the telegram that the agreement might become the background for the firm peace in the Middle East.
